      <title>欧洲央行调查显示欧元区消费者11月通胀预期上升</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/euro-zone-consumers-raise-inflation-expectations-november-ecb-poll-2025-01-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行周二公布的一项调查显示，欧元区家庭11月份通胀预期上调，表明多年的高通胀仍然影响着家庭心理。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/euro-zone-consumers-raise-inflation-expectations-november-ecb-poll-2025-01-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 09:09:07 GMT</pubDate>
